{"tid":948631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"柯P話「兩岸一家親」、「同文同種」係無錯+","createTime":"2018-12-20T08:15:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T15:44:26.000Z","uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"250c353ea8fc94e8d595e2e26c207e0d4fb33824","tid":948631,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T08:15:27.000Z","msg":"沒提兩岸一家親！雙城論壇登場 柯文哲：合作代替對抗<br />\n<br />\n2018/12/20 11:57<br />\n<br />\n我們的頻道 ➔ <a href=\"http://video.ltn.com.tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.ltn.com.tw&d=JToigBLEqFuBXABKqoXuzC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=28460dc0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.ltn.com.tw&h=19188d2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://video.ltn.com.tw</a><br />\n<br />\n這裡也看得到我們 ➔ <a href=\"https://www.dailymotion.com/LibertyTimes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymotion.com%2FLibertyTimes&d=JToigBLEqFuBXABKqoXuzC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=1daf2a8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymotion.com/LibertyTimes</a><br />\n<br />\n台北-上海雙城論壇今（20）日登場，台北市長柯文哲昨日於晚宴上再次提及「兩岸一家親」、「同文同種」，因此引發波瀾。而在今日的演講中，柯文哲表示要以對話代替對抗，只要將人民的福祉擺第一，兩岸就能共同合作。此外，柯文哲今日的演講未再提及「兩岸一家親」。<br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;<br />\n<br />\n台灣海峽兩岸<br />\n即係台灣跟福建(閩)<br />\n大家都係百越族人<br />\n跟台灣原居民亦係近親"},{"pid":"33ab36a609b1dbb949d097e126b84a0abe774ac0","tid":948631,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T08:17:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ec2467bdc9e90d979bfb7d6d77cfc7e77d9366c","tid":948631,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T08:22:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27eb645c5428a982f67a41aaf7c3bd54b55a4f13","tid":948631,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T08:22:59.000Z","msg":"柯文哲「殖民越久越進步」論被指「內心皇民化」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/china/2015/01/150131_taiwan_ko_colonisation